# Modulo dashboard

Escopo
- Indicadores operacionais e visao resumida do negocio.
- Agregacao de KPIs, series e rankings para o usuario.

Rotas e entradas
- Stack: `src/modules/dashboard/presentation/stack/dashboard.stack.tsx`.
- Base path: `/dashboard`.
- Pages:
  - `landing`: `presentation/pages/landing/landing.page`.
  - `home`: `presentation/pages/dashboard/dashboard.page`.

Modelos principais (interfaces)
- `DashboardKpiModel`: id, label, value, changePct.
- `DashboardSeriesPointModel`: key, label, revenue, profit.
- `DashboardServiceSalesModel`: serviceId, serviceName, count, revenue.
- `DashboardPaymentStatusModel`: status (paid/pending/refunded), count, amount.
- `DashboardClientRankModel`: clientName, ordersCount, totalSpent, avgTicket, lastPurchase.
- `DashboardSaleItemModel`: clientName, serviceName, dateTime, amount, status.
- `DashboardQueryModel`: from, to, groupBy (day/week/month).

Services
- `dashboard.service.ts`
  - Gera dados mock com base em periodo.
  - Nao depende de backend atualmente.

Guardrails
- Manter contratos dos modelos para evitar quebrar UI.
- Quando conectar a backend, manter a mesma estrutura de resposta (`DashboardResponse`).
